         |Discover a selection of the best rated smartphones
      .col-lg-4
        img(src="/images/livrelecteurs.jpeg", alt="140x140", class="img-circle", style="width: 140px; height: 140px;")
        h2 Books and E-Books
        p
         |Like to read? We propose you thousands of books and e-book available right now or in pre-order
      .col-lg-4
        img(src="/images/nrj.jpg", alt="140x140", class="img-circle", style="width: 140px; height: 140px;")
        h2 Music
        p
         |You listen to music for hours ans hours ? you can't do without it ? Come discover the artists of the moment !
    hr(class="featurette-divider")
